parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the passenger airbag sensor mat can cause the airbag to malfunction, leading to potential accidents or injuries. If the airbag deploys unnecessarily, it can cause damage to the vehicle and its occupants. Conversely, if the airbag fails to deploy in a crash, it can lead to serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: the passenger airbag off light stays on or off
or the airbag fails to deploy in a crash.

or the airbag fails to deploy in a crash.

symptoms: Doors lock or unlock on their own
doors lock while driving or with the engine off
door locks click on and off automatically
unable to open doors from the inside or outside
door unlock button does not release the mechanism.
